videos.headline: Hopkins throws 31-yard Army TD
videos.description: Kelvin Hopkins Jr. finds Camden Harrison over the middle and Harrison cruises into the end zone for a 31-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: San Jose State WR makes fingertip TD catch
